Title: Free Fields for Any Spin in Relativistic Quantum Mechanics

Authors: D. R. Grigore

Comments: 10 pages, IFA-FT-400, LATEX

A general discussion of the construction of free fields based on Weinberganszatz is provided and various applications appearing in the litterature areconsidered.